'''Bukowa''' {{IPA-pl|[|b|u|'|k|o|w|a|]}} is a [[village]] in the administrative district of [[Gmina Osiek, <U+015A>wi<U+0119>tokrzyskie Voivodeship|Gmina Osiek]], within [[Stasz<U+00F3>w County]], [[<U+015A>wi<U+0119>tokrzyskie Voivodeship]], in south-central [[Poland]]. It lies approximately {{convert|7|km|mi|0}} north of [[Osiek]], {{convert|19|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} east of [[Stasz<U+00F3>w]], and {{convert|67|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} south-east of the regional capital [[Kielce]].<ref name="TERYT">{{cite web |url=http://www.stat.gov.pl/broker/access/prefile/listPreFiles.jspa |title=Central Statistical Office (GUS) - TERYT (National Register of Territorial Land Apportionment Journal) |date=2008-06-01 |language=Polish}}</ref>

